OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772136278
OL,3,CMeasles remains 'real threat' due to
OL,4,Cunvaccinated children, expert warns
OL,6,FThe number of measles cases in London
OL,7,Fcontinues to rise with growing
OL,8,Fconcerns that it is further spreading
OL,9,Finto other regions.
OL,11,FThe latest laboratory figures from the
OL,12,FUK Health Security Agency (UKHSA) have
OL,13,Fconfirmed that 89 children up to the
OL,14,Fage of 14 in London have contracted
OL,15,Fthe disease between January 1 and
OL,16,FFebruary 23.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
