OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772136278
OL,3,CMeasles remains 'real threat' due to
OL,4,Cunvaccinated children, expert warns
OL,6,FIn Enfield, where the outbreak has
OL,7,Fbeen most severe, the number has
OL,8,Fincreased to 59 cases, an increase of
OL,9,Fnine from the previous week (February
OL,10,F16).
OL,12,FThe actual number of cases is expected
OL,13,Fto be higher, but the time lag
OL,14,Finvolved in laboratory testing means
OL,15,Fthey won't be captured in the latest
OL,16,Fdata.
OL,18,FAcross the country there have been 24
OL,19,Fmore cases confirmed in the past week
OL,20,F(158).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
