OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772136278
OL,3,CMeasles remains 'real threat' due to
OL,4,Cunvaccinated children, expert warns
OL,6,FThe majority of cases were in children
OL,7,Faged ten and under, with only 19% of
OL,8,Fcases in those aged 15 and over.
OL,10,FOutside of London, the West Midlands
OL,11,Fhas had 33 cases, with the majority,
OL,12,F28, being in Birmingham. The East
OL,13,FMidlands has the third highest number
OL,14,Fof cases, with eight confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
