PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772136278
OL,3,CMeasles remains 'real threat' due to
OL,4,Cunvaccinated children, expert warns
OL,6,FLondon Region Deputy Director for the
OL,7,FUKHSA, Dr Yimmy Chow is concerned the
OL,8,Fcase numbers will rise if children
OL,9,Faren't vaccinated. He said: "The
OL,10,Fmeasles outbreak in north London
OL,11,Fcontinues and while children remain
OL,12,Funvaccinated, the risk of it spreading
OL,13,Fto other areas remains a real threat.
OL,15,F"Some parents today will be unaware of
OL,16,Fthe terrible harm measles caused to so
OL,17,Fmany children before the introduction
OL,18,Fof a vaccine.
OL,26,@qD@]OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
