OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772136278
OL,3,CMeasles remains 'real threat' due to
OL,4,Cunvaccinated children, expert warns
OL,6,F"Measles can cause pneumonia,
OL,7,Fmeningitis, blindness, seizures and
OL,8,Ftragically sometimes death. Every year
OL,9,Fwe see children in hospital suffering
OL,10,Fneedlessly, sometimes leading to long
OL,11,Fterm complications.
OL,13,F"With a disease as infectious as
OL,14,Fmeasles, it will find those
OL,15,Funvaccinated - there is no room for
OL,16,Fcomplacency. Two doses of the vaccine
OL,17,Fwill give children vital protection.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
